00:44:14.580 --> 00:44:17.379
with the rest of the theme of the document,

00:44:17.379 --> 00:44:23.340
the colors of metals, and also colorize the data.

00:44:23.340 --> 00:44:26.179
So different colors mean different magnitude.

00:44:26.179 --> 00:44:29.179
And we can do that with the data underscore color

00:44:29.179 --> 00:44:32.419
function in the GT package.

00:44:32.419 --> 00:44:35.179
This is going to be a numeric variable.

00:44:35.179 --> 00:44:37.620
So we'll set method to numeric.

00:44:37.620 --> 00:44:43.939
And for the palette, I'm going to use

00:44:43.939 --> 00:44:48.379
